       <p><a href="http://www.universityofcalifornia.edu/sites/default/files/uc_mini_sst.pdf"><img alt="image of students carrying garbage from brochure" height="114" src="_images/sustainability-brochure.png" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" width="140"></a>Read <a href="http://www.universityofcalifornia.edu/sites/default/files/uc_mini_sst.pdf">UC: The living laboratory for sustainability (pdf)</a></p> 
