       <h4>UC Green on Flipboard</h4> 
       <p><a href="http://flip.it/mnHg2"><img alt="uc green flipboard cover" height="135" src="_images/uc-green-flipboard-cover.png" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" width="140"></a>Blue + Gold = Green. The University of California is devoted to healthy people and a healthy planet. <a href="http://flip.it/mnHg2">Read about our latest discoveries in sustainability and green living on Flipboard.</a></p> 
